The '''Mill''' is a building in the [[Advanced Production]] category. It produces [[Flour]] from [[Wheat]].

== Production ==
The Mill consumes 1 [[Wheat]] to produce 1 [[Flour]].

== Upgrades ==
* '''Efficient processing:''' Increases efficiency and speed. Now consumes 3 [[Wheat]] to produce 2 [[Flour]].
* '''Troop inspiration:''' Passively increases damage dealt by and HP of [[Flying]] troops by 5%.